-shadow:0 0 10px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}.contactFormAsside{position:relative;top:-5px;font-style:italic;margin-bottom:25px}p{padding-left:15px}h4{margin-bottom:0}</style></head><body><header><h1>Privacy Policy</h1></header><div><span class="">Last Modified: 11/16/2023, 7:35:31 AM</span></div><h2>Preface</h2><p>I try to collect as little data as possible, and share even less with 3rd parties. Transparency : Honesty : Integrity : Responsibility.</p><section><h2>3rd Party</h2><p>When you interact with the contact page, after your consent, we share your browser session with Google in order to test if you are a bot.</p><h4>Google RECAPTCHA</h4><p>Google provides a service called RECAPTCHA that helps secure a website against bot attacks. In the sections of the site protected by RECAPTCHA, we will share your browsing session with Google. Google will have access to all of the information as if you had visited the google website, along with the information that you had visited our site. Also, there is no way for us to garuntee that Google didn't capture the information entered into the forms on the website.</p><p>Google provides its own, separate <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="https://policies.google.com/terms">Terms of Service</a></p><h4>YouTube</h4><p>To embed YouTube videos on our site, we have to share some of your browsing session with YouTube.</p><p>Google provides its own, separate <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> and <a href="https://policies.google.com/terms">Terms of Service</a></p></section><section><h2>The Forms</h2><h3 class="contactFormAsside">In regards to the form: Contact</h3><p>The contact form collects emails and general query information.</p><h3>How we use this Data</h3><p>I use this information to answer your queries.</p><h3>Who will see this data at our company</h3><p>Me, or other people I work with who have credentials to log in as an administrator to this website.</p><h3>Who we share this data with</h3><p>No third parties without your expressed permission.</p><h3>Where we store this data</h3><p>It is stored encrypted on our server.</p></section><h2>Updates</h2><p>Updated to this privacy policy will be published here. The last modified date will be present at the top. And you will be notified where possible and appropriate.</p><br><br><a href=".">Return Home</a></body></html>